From: Harini Katakam <harini.katakam@xilinx.com>
Date: Mon, 17 Mar 2014 13:16:49 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 091/509] SPI: cadence: Readability change in
 transfer_one_message

https://github.com/analogdevicesinc/linux.git xcomm_zynq
commit 1060b63f21114d84ec89d8fd92cffd640aa54bdb

Change if statement in transfer_one_message to improve readability.

Signed-off-by: Harini Katakam <harinik@xilinx.com>
Signed-off-by: Michal Simek <michal.simek@xilinx.com>
Signed-off-by: Zhong Hongbo <hongbo.zhong@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/spi/spi-cadence.c |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/spi/spi-cadence.c b/drivers/spi/spi-cadence.c
index 48093af..836af80 100644
--- a/drivers/spi/spi-cadence.c
+++ b/drivers/spi/spi-cadence.c
@@ -535,7 +535,7 @@ static int cdns_transfer_one_message(struct spi_master *master,
 		cdns_spi_chipselect(spi, 0);
 	}
 
-	if (!(status == 0 && cs_change))
+	if (status || !cs_change)
 		cdns_spi_chipselect(spi, 0);
 
 	msg->status = status;
